      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can you make it a bit more specific though? like, i want him to describe the people themselves more in detail. maybe talk about how they lack the structure of modern society or how their way of life seems almost animalistic compared to europe. it'll help show the contrast he's feeling.",
